    <h1>Other big pay&#xAD;days for lo&#xAD;cal ath&#xAD;letes</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20201125/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-11-25"><time>2020-11-25</time></a>
        - <span>SPORT</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
